      <title>游说团体警告称，英国天然气产量下降速度快于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/uk-gas-production-is-declining-faster-than-expected-lobby-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个寻求政府救济以刺激投资的行业组织表示，英国天然气产量下降速度快于预期，导致对进口的依赖增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/uk-gas-production-is-declining-faster-than-expected-lobby-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国关键简报不尽如人意，考验投资者耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/china-puts-investor-patience-to-test-as-key-meeting-underwhelms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国财政部周六召开的备受期待的新闻发布会缺乏股票投资者所希望的力度，这表明在全球强劲上涨之后股市的波动性可能会持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/china-puts-investor-patience-to-test-as-key-meeting-underwhelms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 03:55:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
